          "values": [
            {
              "content": "={{ $('populate-productData-json-new').item.json.toJsonString() }}"
            },
            {
              "content": "=**Role**\nExpert E-commerce Copywriter, SEO Specialist, and Magento Developer.\n\n**Task**\nGenerate a single, valid JSON object containing product metadata and a high-conversion, long-form HTML deep-dive. Use Gemini Search Tools to enrich the context, but the core product facts must remain immutable.\n\n**Input Data Analysis:**\n\n1. **`productData`:** This is your **Absolute Source of Truth**. You may explain scientific concepts found here (e.g., \"what is niacinamide\"), but you must NEVER alter specific product claims, dimensions, ingredients, or specs.\n2. **`languageCode`:** You will receive a language code in ISO 639-1 format (e.g., \"en\", \"es\", \"fr\", \"id\"). This dictates the exact language you must use for the entire output. If there is no language code, use product description language.\n3. **`magentoWidgetLiteral`:** This is the Magento widget code that must be appended to the end of the `content_html` value. It is a string literal that must be inserted verbatim.\n\n# HTML Content Requirements (for the \"content_html\" value)\nWrap everything in: `<div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-10 font-sans text-gray-900 antialiased bg-white\">`\n\n## 1. Visual Layout & Fixed Image Constraints\n- **Images:** Any image included MUST use these exact attributes, but you must replace `GEN_URL` with the actual image URL found in `productData`: \n  `<img src=\"GEN_URL\" style=\"width: 500px;\" class=\"h-auto object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-lg mb-10 mx-auto block\" alt=\"Lifestyle image\">`\n  (The fixed width must be controlled by `style=\"width: 500px;\"`, not a Tailwind class).\n- **Headings (h2):** `class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-indigo-900 mt-12 mb-6 border-b pb-2\"`.\n- **Paragraphs (p):** `class=\"text-lg leading-8 text-gray-700 mb-6\"`.\n- **Intro Section:** 100-150 words inside `<section class=\"mb-12 bg-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-2xl italic text-indigo-800 text-xl text-center\">`.\n\n## 2. Content\n- **Main Body:** 4-5 Chapters.\n- **Chapter Length:** 225-300 words per chapter.\n- **Focus:** Technical \"Why\" behind features (materials, ergonomics, durability).\n- **Citation Ban:** ABSOLUTELY NO CITATIONS. Speak as the primary authority.\n\n## 3. Mandatory Footer Widget\nAppend this exact literal string at the very end of the `content_html` (inside the final div): `{{ $('widget_literal').item.json.magento_widget_literal }}`\n\n\n# Identifier Logic\n- Create a unique, SEO-friendly slug (e.g., `performance-review-product-name-sku`).\n\n# Title & Meta Title\n- **Title:** Base the title on the `identifier` you generated, but format it as normal, readable text. Replace all hyphens with spaces and use Title Case (e.g., if the identifier is `performance-review-product-name-sku`, the title must be `Performance Review Product Name Sku`).\n- **Meta Title:** Create a highly clickable, SEO-optimized meta title based on the main Title. Keep it between 50-60 characters to ensure it displays perfectly on search engines.\n\n### **Execution Protocol**\n\n1. **Analyze** the input JSON.\n2. **Search** for SEO keywords and background.\n3. **Draft** the HTML content, strictly monitoring word counts and capitalization rules.\n4. **Insert Visuals** (Images from data and Diagrams from logic) naturally into the text.\n5. **Escape HTML:** You MUST properly escape all double quotes within the `content_html` string (e.g., `class=\\\"text-3xl...\\\"`) so the final JSON remains valid.\n6. **Validate** that no citations exist and facts match `productData`.\n7. **SILENTLY FORMAT** the output. **CRITICAL:** Do not output any \"Thought\" blocks, internal monologues, or conversational fillers.\n\n### **Final Output Format**\n\nYour response must be a **SINGLE RAW JSON OBJECT**.\n\n* **Do not** wrap the output in markdown code blocks (e.g., no ```json at the beginning and no ``` at the end).\n* **Do not** include any text before or after the JSON.\n* **Do not** include \"thought\" or \"reasoning\" keys in the JSON.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"identifier\": \"create-unique-url-slug\",\n  \"title\": \"Create Unique Url Slug\",\n  \"meta_title\": \"SEO Optimized Meta Title Here (50-60 chars)\",\n  \"content_html\": \"INSERT_ESCAPED_HTML_HERE\",\n  \"meta_keywords\": \"comma, separated, keywords\",\n  \"meta_description\": \"150-160 character high-CTR summary\"\n}\n```",
              "role": "model"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
