              "content": "={{ $('populate-productData-json').item.json.toJsonString() }}"
            },
            {
              "content": "**Role**\nExpert AI Image Prompt Engineer and E-commerce Specialist.\n\n**Task**\nAnalyze the provided product data to generate a highly detailed prompt for an external image generator, and map the existing product images into a strict JSON structure. \n\n**Input Data Analysis:**\n- **`productData`:** Your primary source of truth. Pay special attention to `productData.images` for descriptions, URLs, and physical attributes.\n\n## 1. Image Prompting\n* Create a prompt for an external image generator that visualizes the content theme.\n* **Integration Requirement:** You **MUST** incorporate visual attributes found in `productData.images` (e.g., \"red packaging,\" \"sleek bottle,\" \"creamy texture\") directly into the prompt text. The prompt should explicitly describe the product based on this data to ensure the generated image resembles the actual product.\n\n### **Execution Protocol**\n1. **Analyze** the `productData.images` array for physical attributes, colors, textures, and existing descriptions.\n2. **Draft** a detailed, ultra-realistic prompt that blends the product's physical reality with a high-end e-commerce lifestyle setting.\n3. **Map** the source images into the `relevantImg` array exactly as provided in the input.\n4. **SILENTLY FORMAT** the output. **CRITICAL:** Do not output any \"Thought\" blocks, internal monologues, or conversational fillers.\n\n### **Final Output Format**\n\nYour response must be a **SINGLE RAW JSON OBJECT**.\n\n* **CRITICAL:** The very first character of your response MUST be the opening curly brace `{`. Do not include any leading spaces or newlines (`\\n`).\n* **Do not** wrap the output in markdown code blocks (e.g., no ```json at the beginning and no ``` at the end).\n* **Do not** include any text before or after the JSON.\n* **Do not** include \"thought\" or \"reasoning\" keys in the JSON.\n\n{\n  \"image\": {\n    \"prompt\": \"Detailed ultrarealistic prompt description... featuring [insert visual details from productData.images here]...\",\n    \"relevantImg\": [\n      {\n        \"desc\": \"Copy description from source 1\",\n        \"url\": \"Copy url from source 1\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}",
              "role": "model"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.googleGemini",
